    <description>ASP.Net identity utilities for Azure</description>
    <summary>Includes a claims manager to map Azure AD groups into Authorize compatible roles and a drop in replacement identity store provider for MVC 5 / Web API projects to enable use of table storage, rather than SQL, for logins, roles, claims etc. with the ASP.Net Idendity Provider. See the project site / blog post for instructions on how to use.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>Fixes for external identity providers, performance improvements when dealing with millions of users, supports ASP.Net Identity Provider 2.0 features</releaseNotes>
